---
title: Ginger-Soy Beef Stir-Fry with Broccoli & Peanuts
description: Whip up a classic stir-fry using an easy ginger-soy sauce plus plenty of colourful veggies and tender beef strips. It's simple, fast and tasty and beats takeaway any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bf4a0e2ae08b56bf03b58c3-ee1bcc72.jpg
